Meta-Analysis (Collapsed Model)

Liam A. Doyle

2024-07-05

Project Description

This is an R Markdown file that documents for some of the analyses conducted for the first study in my meta-analysis. Specifically, this file documents the multi-level meta-analytic model conducted for the effect of psychopathy on behaviours across all economic games (i.e., the collapsed model).
